SEARCH
Package com.grassnext.grassnextserver.topodata

Class TopoDataParser

java.lang.Object
com.grassnext.grassnextserver.topodata.TopoDataParser
@Service public class TopoDataParser extends Object
The TopoDataParser class is responsible for parsing and processing data read from topo detectors from input files, extracting relevant header, main, extra and remaining time data, and mapping it to appropriate entities for persistence and further processing.
